---
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---
<SiteLayout page="ahora" lang="en" title="Now — Danilo Diez">

  <div class="section-header">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">Now · June 2026</p>
    <h1 class="section-title">What I'm doing now.</h1>
    <p class="section-lead">A living page, updated monthly. Inspired by Derek Sivers's /now movement.</p>
  </div>

  <hr class="rule">

  <div class="now-block">
    <p class="now-label">Work</p>
    <p class="now-text">Building AI features at LenioLabs — currently deep in voice-recognition interfaces for Vocale. Also putting time into SomosCool, trying to make it something real.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="now-block">
    <p class="now-label">Reading</p>
    <p class="now-text"><em>Philosophical Investigations</em> — Wittgenstein. Slowly. Rereading <em>The Myth of Sisyphus</em> for the third time.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="now-block">
    <p class="now-label">Listening</p>
    <p class="now-text">Mostly Satie and Piazzolla. Trying to understand how both use silence as structure. On the rock side: Hum's <em>Downward is Heavenward</em> on repeat.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="now-block">
    <p class="now-label">Outdoors</p>
    <p class="now-text">Planning a night hike up Cerro Monje for August. Training on shorter trails around Posadas on weekends.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="now-block">
    <p class="now-label">Writing</p>
    <p class="now-text">Trying to write more. Starting this garden was part of that. No pressure to publish — just to plant.</p>
  </div>

  <hr class="rule">
  <p style="font-size:16px;color:var(--faint);">Last updated: June 2026 · Posadas, Misiones 🧉</p>

</SiteLayout>
